"confirmation of a quotation or a website sale can triggers the creation of a "
"delivery order to your customer in the <strong>Inventory </strong>app. You "
"can\n"
"        always see how much of each product you have available in the "
"Inventory app menu, as well as on each individual product form."
msgstr ""
"Ko izdelke ponujate na spletu, se prepričajte, da imate dovolj zalog. "
"Potrditev ponudbe ali spletne prodaje lahko sproži ustvarjanje naročila za "
"dostavo vaši stranki v aplikaciji <strong>Zaloga</strong>. Vedno\n"
"        lahko vidite, koliko posameznega izdelka imate na voljo v meniju "
"aplikacije Zaloga, pa tudi na posameznem obrazcu za izdelek."

